              <h2>Goals</h2>
            </div>
            <p>
              This is where the dough hits the pan. We set the expectations of
              what you're going to learn.
            </p>
          </li>
          <li
            class="box rounded mx-auto flow prose"
            style="--spot-color: var(--purple1000); --spot-color-text: var(--purple300);"
          >
            <div>
              <div class="font-hero font-weight-light">Lesson 3</div>
              <h2>Storytelling</h2>
            </div>
            <p>
              This is where the dough hits the pan. We set the expectations of
              what you're going to learn.
            </p>
          </li>
          <li
            class="box rounded mx-auto flow prose"
            style="--spot-color: var(--purple1000); --spot-color-text: var(--purple300);"
          >
            <div>
              <div class="font-hero font-weight-light">Lesson 4</div>
              <h2>Who are successful franchise partners?</h2>
            </div>
            <p>
              This is where the dough hits the pan. We set the expectations of
              what you're going to learn.
            </p>
          </li>
          <li
            class="box rounded mx-auto flow prose"
            style="--spot-color: var(--purple1000); --spot-color-text: var(--purple300);"
          >
            <div>
              <div class="font-hero font-weight-light">Lesson 5</div>
              <h2>Voice &amp; tone</h2>
            </div>
            <p>
              This is where the dough hits the pan. We set the expectations of
              what you're going to learn.
            </p>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <div class="box w-3/4 mx-auto">
          <a
            href="https://buy.stripe.com/5kA03Sbxb9DG4akbII"
            target="_blank"
            class="button purple-button">Buy now</a
          >
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
    <section class="region wrapper">
      <div class="switcher">
        <div class="prose flow">
          <h2>Community</h2>
          <p>
            We have created a professional community solely for dessert
            franchises. Build long lasting healthy habits with peers in the
            dessert franchise space. Join us for events with coaches and experts
            in all aspects of the busienss. Discuss the Leader &amp; Unit Growth
