            <li>Join early to get exclusive 1-on-1 time</li>
            <li>Accountability partners</li>
            <li>Build long last relationships, and habits</li>
            <li>Course owners get VIP access</li>
            <li>Share your experience, and gain perspective</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="box flex justify-center items-center">
          <a
            href="https://discord.gg/gv7uSYekbt"
            target="_blank"
            class="button"
          >
            Join now!</a
